## 📂 Project Structure

```text
autoclick/
│
├── flow_builder_pro.py        # Main entry point for the Tkinter desktop application.
│
├── core/                      # Core automation and helper utilities.
│   ├── automation.py          # Windows API wrapper (mouse, keyboard, active window).
│   └── payload.py             # Variable resolution and template interpolation logic.
│
├── models/                    # Visual models representing elements on the canvas.
│   ├── node.py                # Visual node logic, theme styling, and action handlers.
│   └── connection.py          # Catmull-Rom spline line connection and waypoint editor.
│
├── connectors/                # External integration mixins.
│   ├── api.py                 # REST HTTP Request connector.
│   └── database.py            # PostgreSQL, MySQL, and SQLite drivers.
│
└── ui/                        # Graphical interface mixins.
    ├── canvas_panel.py        # Central canvas container.
    ├── canvas_interactions.py  # Dragging, panning, and zoom controls.
    ├── left_panel.py          # Sidebar listing available nodes.
    ├── right_panel.py         # Node property editors and configuration.
    ├── connection_dialogs.py  # Management panels for saved database and API connections.
    ├── coordinate_capture.py  # Invisible full-screen capture layer for mouse coordinates.
    └── tray_icon.py           # Tray icon management and global hotkey binding.
```

